That won't make me know something I don't.

328
00:30:28,012 --> 00:30:31,197
你快告诉他 我可是你外甥啊
Just tell him. I am your nephew.

329
00:30:31,348 --> 00:30:33,324
表的
No, just a distant nephew.

330
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:35,576
我 血浓于水啊
Don't.- Blood is thicker than water.

331
00:30:35,728 --> 00:30:39,455
给点提示呗 那一箱金子
Give me a hint.- That box of gold.

332
00:30:39,606 --> 00:30:42,542
你说 那个雕塑作坊 往下说
You mean in the statue workshop?- Go on.

333
00:30:42,735 --> 00:30:45,962
那人打电话 让我去接箱子
That man called me and asked me to pick up the box.

334
00:30:46,113 --> 00:30:47,964
我不知道里面是金子啊
I didn't know there was gold inside.

335
00:30:48,115 --> 00:30:51,884
你把箱子放哪了 那人 让我送到
Where did you take the box?- That man asked me to...

336
00:30:52,036 --> 00:30:54,804
海天大厦地下停车场
...deliver it to the underground parking lot of Haitian Mansion...

337
00:30:54,955 --> 00:30:56,889
一辆面包车的旁边啦
...and drop it off next to a van.

338
00:30:57,041 --> 00:31:00,018
金刚 看好他们两个 好
King Kong, watch over them.- Okay.

339
00:31:00,169 --> 00:31:04,063
越南仔 咱俩找箱子去 走
Vietnamese, let's go find the box.- Okay.

340
00:31:05,466 --> 00:31:10,069
如果你敢骗我 弄死我
If you lie to me...- You can kill me.

341
00:31:30,658 --> 00:31:32,842
你吃什么
You want to eat?

342
00:31:32,993 --> 00:31:36,304
偷我们的黄金 害得我们就吃这
You stole our gold,so we have to eat this.

343
00:33:21,810 --> 00:33:23,619
砸呀
Do it!

344
00:33:32,946 --> 00:33:36,466
又来呀 你松手 你松手 松手 松手啊
What are you doing?Let go, let go! Let go!

345
00:33:36,617 --> 00:33:38,217
一起松啊 好
We let go together.- Fine.

346
00:33:38,369 --> 00:33:40,470
一 二 三
One, two, three.

347
00:33:44,041 --> 00:33:46,559
链子给我啊 给 给 给
Give me the necklace.- Here.

348
00:33:46,710 --> 00:33:48,895
快点 快跑啊
Come on. Run!

349
00:33:49,046 --> 00:33:51,022
 松手 松手 松手
Let go, let go, let go!

350
00:34:08,649 --> 00:34:12,627
都怪你 大皇宫呢
It's all your fault.What about the Grand Palace?

351
00:34:12,778 --> 00:34:14,587
你一来泰国就这么多事
You have caused me so much trouble.

352
00:34:14,738 --> 00:34:16,464
我还没说你是丧门星呢
You are such a bird of ill omen.

353
00:34:16,615 --> 00:34:19,550
现在去哪啊 我得把这个给阿香送去啊
Where are you going now?- I have to give this to Xiang.

354
00:34:19,702 --> 00:34:24,138
你疯啦 顺便让泰哥 和我们在那里碰个头
Are you out of your mind?- I'll ask Tai to meet us there.

355
00:34:24,290 --> 00:34:26,974
我可不想死的糊里糊涂的啦
I don't want to die for no good reason.

356
00:34:27,126 --> 00:34:29,602
那几个匪徒 怎么会知道我们在哪
How did the gangsters know where we were?

357
00:34:29,753 --> 00:34:32,522
什么意思啊 匪徒身上会有手铐
What are you talking about?- How did they get the handcuffs?

358
00:34:32,673 --> 00:34:35,316
你是说 警察里面有他们的内线
You mean there is a mole in the police?

359
00:34:35,467 --> 00:34:37,235
那也不可能是泰哥啦
Even so, it can't be Tai.

360
00:34:37,386 --> 00:34:41,864
你信他吗 他肯定不会骗我啦
You trust him?- I'm sure he won't lie to me.

361
00:34:42,057 --> 00:34:43,908
你猜 这车子能动吗
Do you think the bike is still working?

362
00:34:44,059 --> 00:34:46,911
废话真多 管他要份案情报告
Cut the crap.Ask him for the case report.

363
00:34:47,062 --> 00:34:49,956
中文的 干什么
In Chinese.- Why?

364
00:34:50,107 --> 00:34:52,959
你不想知道你杀了谁吗
Don't you want to know who you killed?

365
00:34:59,783 --> 00:35:02,135
快进来 快点
Come in. Hurry up!

366
00:35:02,286 --> 00:35:04,345
你们怎么来了 整个曼谷都在通缉你们
What are you doing here? You are wanted in the whole Bangkok.

367
00:35:05,289 --> 00:35:07,557
生日快乐 神经病
Happy birthday.- You're crazy.

368
00:35:08,083 --> 00:35:10,143
我没杀人你信吗
I didn't kill anyone.Do you believe me?

369
00:35:10,294 --> 00:35:12,603
我信你没有用 要警察信你才行啊
So what if I believe you? You have to make the police believe you.

370
00:35:12,755 --> 00:35:15,148
所以我才约泰哥来这里问个清楚啊
So I want to meet Tai here to find out.

371
00:35:15,299 --> 00:35:17,567
那金子到底是不是你们偷的 我
Did you steal the gold or not?- I...

372
00:35:24,183 --> 00:35:25,616
是泰哥
Is it Tai?

373
00:35:25,768 --> 00:35:27,910
快上去
Go upstairs.

374
00:35:33,067 --> 00:35:34,584
你们找谁
What do you want?

375
00:35:34,735 --> 00:35:38,338
你是阿香吧 我们是唐仁的朋友
You are Xiang, right?We are friends of Tang Ren.

376
00:35:38,489 --> 00:35:41,257
唐仁是谁 别装了
Who is Tang Ren?- Drop the act.

377
00:35:41,408 --> 00:35:44,010
他不最爱你吗 你们到底谁啊
Aren't you the love of his life?- Who the heck are you?

378
00:35:44,161 --> 00:35:47,764
我们是 唐仁的 同伙
We are Tang Ren's partners.

379
00:35:50,084 --> 00:35:54,395
快进来 快点
Come in. Hurry up!

380
00:35:56,548 --> 00:35:59,317
你们真的偷金子了 他没分给你吗
Did you really steal the gold?- Didn't he share it with you?

381
00:35:59,468 --> 00:36:01,402
分了呀
Yes.

382
00:36:01,595 --> 00:36:03,738
漂亮吧
Isn't it pretty?

383
00:36:05,307 --> 00:36:08,993
他也太抠了吧 就给你这么一点
He is so cheap. You deserve more.

384
00:36:09,144 --> 00:36:11,329
到底偷了多少 新闻上没说啊
They didn't say how much you stole in the news.

385
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:14,582
他在哪呢 我让他亲自跟你说
Where is he?I'll ask him to tell you himself.

386
00:36:41,593 --> 00:36:44,529
非逼我见面
Why does he have to meet me here?

387
00:36:44,680 --> 00:36:47,824
这要是被别人看见了 我这警察还做不做了
If anybody sees this,I will be fired.

388
00:36:48,100 --> 00:36:50,159
人呢
Where is he?

389
00:36:58,444 --> 00:37:00,503
黄SIR
Huang.

390
00:37:00,654 --> 00:37:02,672
快上去
Go upstairs.

391
00:37:08,370 --> 00:37:12,849
HAPPY BIRTHDAY 谢谢
Happy birthday.- Thank you.

392
00:37:23,010 --> 00:37:25,528
嘘
Quiet!

393
00:37:37,608 --> 00:37:39,584
嘘
Quiet!

394
00:37:40,569 --> 00:37:43,338
你一个人在家 对啊
Are you home alone?- Yes.

395
00:37:43,489 --> 00:37:45,798
没有人陪你过生日啊
Nobody is celebrating your birthday with you?

396
00:37:45,949 --> 00:37:48,217
一大把年纪了过什么生日啊
I'm too old for that.

397
00:37:52,623 --> 00:37:54,766
谁 没谁
Who was that?- No one.

398
00:37:54,917 --> 00:37:56,684
不对
No way.

399
00:37:57,419 --> 00:38:00,646
黄SIR 上面真的没人
Detective Huang,there is nobody up there.

400
00:38:01,131 --> 00:38:03,107
黄SIR
Detective Huang.

401
00:38:09,431 --> 00:38:11,199
这谁啊
Who is he?

402
00:38:11,934 --> 00:38:13,826
我表哥 你不是说没人吗
My cousin.- You said there's nobody here.

403
00:38:13,978 --> 00:38:16,746
他不是人
He is nobody.

404
00:38:18,482 --> 00:38:20,917
傻的
He is retarded.

405
00:38:23,821 --> 00:38:25,588
黄SIR 知道你忙 就不送你了
I won't see you out since you are so busy.

406
00:38:25,739 --> 00:38:27,924
有机会来我们夜上海玩 就在隔壁的
Come to Night In Shanghai sometime. I'm right next door.

407
00:38:28,075 --> 00:38:31,386
对了 你今天特别帅 拜拜
By the way, you are so handsome.Bye bye.

408
00:38:45,384 --> 00:38:47,735
他们是谁呀 唐仁同伙
Who are they?- Tang Ren's partners.

409
00:38:47,886 --> 00:38:50,905
什么同伙 偷金店的同伙
Partners for what?- The gold shop burglary.

410
00:38:51,056 --> 00:38:53,449
他们不是我同伙啊 我们就是他同伙
They are not my partners.- We are.

411
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:56,577
金店真的是你偷的 金店不是我偷的
Did you really steal the gold?- No, I didn't.

412
00:38:56,729 --> 00:38:58,955
我们一起偷的 你胡说
We did it together.- Nonsense!

413
00:38:59,106 --> 00:39:01,374
那人也是你们杀的 人是他杀的
You killed the man, too?- He killed him.

414
00:39:01,525 --> 00:39:03,876
不是我杀的 就是你杀的
No, I didn't.- Yes, you did.

415
00:39:04,028 --> 00:39:05,962
不是我杀的 就是你杀的
No, I didn't.- Yes, you did.

416
00:39:06,113 --> 00:39:08,506
人真的是你杀的 人真的不是我杀的
You really killed him?- No, I didn't.

417
00:39:08,657 --> 00:39:11,843
金子也不是我偷的 我根本就没有同伙
And I didn't stole the gold.I don't have any partners.

418
00:39:12,661 --> 00:39:16,889
那 我是谁 我知道你是谁啊
So, who am I?- I know who you are.

419
00:39:17,041 --> 00:39:19,392
他知道你是谁啦 那他们到底是谁啊
He knows who you are.- But who the heck are they?

420
00:39:19,668 --> 00:39:22,562
对啊 你们到底是谁呀
Yes. Who the heck are you?

421
00:39:24,465 --> 00:39:27,191
成功了没有 没有
Is it done?- No.

422
00:39:34,183 --> 00:39:36,159
跟我来
Come with me.

423
00:39:41,690 --> 00:39:44,167
黄SIR 你怎么又来了
Detective Huang,what brings you here again?

424
00:39:44,318 --> 00:39:46,669
那个 楼上只有我表哥
There is only my cousin upstairs.

425
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:49,255
真的没有别人了
Nobody else.

426
00:40:01,001 --> 00:40:03,436
大变活人
He shows up out of thin air.

427
00:40:03,587 --> 00:40:06,105
这是我另外一个表哥 二表哥
He is my other cousin.- Second cousin.

428
00:40:06,256 --> 00:40:09,233
你到底有几个表哥
How many cousins do you have?

429
00:40:16,183 --> 00:40:20,161
那刚才那个大表哥呢
Where is your eldest cousin?

430
00:40:29,947 --> 00:40:32,715
三表哥
Your third cousin?

431
00:40:54,054 --> 00:40:59,659
HI HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU
Happy Birthday to you.

432
00:40:59,810 --> 00:41:05,456
HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU
Happy Birthday to you.

433
00:41:05,607 --> 00:41:09,168
SURPRISE HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU
Surprise!- Happy Birthday to you.

434
00:41:13,866 --> 00:41:15,550
谢谢
Thank you, guys.

435
00:41:15,701 --> 00:41:19,095
表妹 今天这个生日你一定会很惊喜
You must feel surprised today.

436
00:41:19,246 --> 00:41:22,473
祝你幸福 谢谢 谢谢你们
Be happy.- Thank you, guys.

437
00:41:22,625 --> 00:41:25,184
表哥还有事 我先走了
I have something else to do.I have to go.

438
00:41:26,295 --> 00:41:28,146
二表哥 三表哥再见
Goodbye, cousins.

439
00:41:28,297 --> 00:41:31,149
生日快乐 大表哥再见
Happy Birthday to you.- Goodbye, eldest cousin.

440
00:41:39,058 --> 00:41:45,580
阿香啊你的口味真的太重了
Xiang, your taste of men is so special.

441
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:50,793
那个黄SIR 我送你吧
Detective Huang, I'll see you out.

442
00:41:52,446 --> 00:41:54,964
泰哥 这是我最后一次帮你了
Tai.- This is the last time I help you.

443
00:41:55,157 --> 00:41:58,426
你要的东西
I've got you the things you need.

444
00:41:58,577 --> 00:42:00,136
船都帮你找好了 时间 地点都在里面
The time and place are all in here.

445
00:42:00,287 --> 00:42:02,597
泰哥 什么都不要讲了
Tai.- Don't say anything.

446
00:42:02,748 --> 00:42:05,433
我只能帮你到这里了
I can't help you anymore.I don't want to see you again...

447
00:42:05,584 --> 00:42:08,311
最好这辈子都不要再见了 保重吧
...for the rest of my life.Take care.

448
00:42:08,629 --> 00:42:10,563
泰哥
Tai.

449
00:42:10,714 --> 00:42:13,566
这么多年感情 无以为报
I have nothing to repay you for all these years' of brotherhood.

450
00:42:13,717 --> 00:42:17,236
传家宝送给你留个念想啦 什么鬼呀
Keep my heirloom as a token.- What the heck is this?

451
00:42:17,388 --> 00:42:18,946
开过光 很灵的
It's been blessed and efficacious.

452
00:42:19,098 --> 00:42:20,907
开车不用系安全带啦
With it, you can drive without fastening the seatbelt.

453
00:42:21,058 --> 00:42:23,785
我还是系上点比较好啊
I'd better fasten it.

454
00:42:30,025 --> 00:42:32,919
你真没杀人 当然 我真没有杀人啦
You really didn't kill that man?- Of course I didn't.

455
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:36,297
那你去那干嘛 我那天在打牌
So why did you go there?- I was playing mahjong...

456
00:42:36,448 --> 00:42:39,133
接到一个陌生人的电话 你好
...and I got a phone callfrom a stranger.

457
00:42:39,285 --> 00:42:42,637
电话那人 让我四月十四日晚十二点
The caller asked me to go to Sompat Workshop...

458
00:42:42,788 --> 00:42:46,099
到颂帕工坊 拉尊佛像
...at 12pm on April 14th to pick up a Buddha statue...

459
00:42:46,250 --> 00:42:48,935
送到海天大厦停车场
...and drop it off at the parking lot of Haitian Mansion.

460
00:42:49,086 --> 00:42:51,813
还说 那个 会把酬劳给我
And he said he would pay me.

461
00:42:52,089 --> 00:42:54,440
那人让我填了一张取货单
That man asked me to fill out a carrier's note...

462
00:42:54,591 --> 00:42:56,567
然后就把钱给我啦
...and gave me the money.

463
00:42:56,719 --> 00:42:59,862
我走时那人没死啊
The man was still alive when I left.

464
00:43:05,936 --> 00:43:07,412
箱子呢
Where is the box?

465
00:43:07,563 --> 00:43:10,206
按规定 送到海天大厦停车场
I delivered it to the parking lot of Haitian Mansion as asked.

466
00:43:10,357 --> 00:43:12,875
那里只有一辆车在等啊
There was only one van waiting.

467
00:43:13,068 --> 00:43:16,379
你没见着收货人 没有啊
Did you see the consignee?- No, I didn't.

468
00:43:16,530 --> 00:43:19,340
那人直接让我把箱子放在车旁边
That man asked me to put the box next to the van.

469
00:43:19,491 --> 00:43:21,509
那地方 前高后下
That place is higher at front and lower in the rear.

470
00:43:21,660 --> 00:43:24,012
阴气太重啦 一看就是不祥之地嘛
It is so gloomy.I'm sure it's a jinx.

471
00:43:24,163 --> 00:43:27,056
谁愿意久留呢 你没打开箱子看看啊
So I left right away.- Didn't you open the box?

472
00:43:27,207 --> 00:43:31,310
那箱子是封死的嘛 谁知道里面是黄金呢
It was sealed. Who would have thought there was gold inside?

473
00:43:32,838 --> 00:43:35,314
有意思 有意思
Interesting.- Interesting?

474
00:43:35,466 --> 00:43:40,194
从证据看 你就是凶手
According to the evidence,you are the murderer.

475
00:43:40,346 --> 00:43:41,946
我不是凶手啦
No, I am not.

476
00:43:42,139 --> 00:43:45,616
那人怎么死的 我哪知道他怎么死的
So how did he die?- How would I know?

477
00:43:49,438 --> 00:43:52,290
你不想知道真相是什么吗
Don't you want to know the truth?

478
00:43:52,441 --> 00:43:55,084
我想活下去啦 别走
I want to survive.- Stay here.

479
00:43:55,235 --> 00:43:58,755
不走干嘛 破案
Why should I stay?- Solve the case.

480
00:44:01,367 --> 00:44:04,886
没发烧啊 这孩子怎么还说胡话了呢
You are not having a fever.Why do you talk nonsense?

481
00:44:05,037 --> 00:44:07,221
多好玩啊 你别扯淡了
It's fun.- Nonsense!

482
00:44:07,539 --> 00:44:10,308
那我的命在陪你玩 要玩你自己玩
I'm risking my life.You are on your own now.

483
00:44:10,459 --> 00:44:12,268
我必须走
I have to leave.

484
00:44:13,420 --> 00:44:15,980
船来啦 老子要闪人啦
The boat is here.I'm getting out of here.

485
00:44:27,017 --> 00:44:31,120
再见THAILAND THAILAND
Goodbye, Thailand. Thailand.

486
00:44:34,024 --> 00:44:38,211
我不知道 我回去 怎么向父老乡亲们交代
I don't know how to explain to the folks.

487
00:44:38,362 --> 00:44:42,090
出来混得好好的 怎么突然就回去了呢
Why do I suddenly go back while I have a good life here?

488
00:44:42,241 --> 00:44:45,885
我想想 这辈子再也见不到阿香
To think that I'll never see Xiang again...

489
00:44:46,036 --> 00:44:52,141
我的心就像刀割一样疼 刀割一样你懂吗
...I am torn with grief.Torn with grief, you know?

490
00:45:06,223 --> 00:45:08,157
快 快 快 马上走了
Come on, hurry up.We are leaving.

491
00:45:08,350 --> 00:45:11,744
他们也去中国 谁说我们去中国
Are they going to China, too?- Who told you that?

492
00:45:11,895 --> 00:45:14,831
那去哪里呀 赤道几内亚
So where are you going?- Equatorial Guinea.

493
00:45:14,982 --> 00:45:18,167
什么 赤道几内亚
What?- Equatorial Guinea.

494
00:45:19,278 --> 00:45:23,381
赤道几内亚是什么地方 非洲吧
Where is that?- I think it's in Africa.

495
00:45:23,991 --> 00:45:29,095
我们会死在那里吗 也许 我们会 死船上
Will we die there?- Maybe we will die on the boat.

496
00:45:31,457 --> 00:45:34,142
快上船 快点 NO NO NO
Get on board.- No, no, no.

497
00:45:34,293 --> 00:45:37,103
你们到底走不走 不走啦
Are you coming or not?- No, we are not.

498
00:45:37,254 --> 00:45:38,771
不走啦
