And after you left,nobody went in.

670
01:04:48,755 --> 01:04:50,814
而且 那就只有一个入口
Besides,there is only one entrance.

671
01:04:50,965 --> 01:04:54,443
所以呢就怀疑我是凶手 要么就是
So you think I'm the murderer?- Or...

672
01:04:54,594 --> 01:04:57,279
谁 鬼
Who?- A ghost.

673
01:04:57,430 --> 01:04:59,906
鬼和咖啡馆有什么关系啊
What does the ghost have to do with the coffee shop?

674
01:05:00,058 --> 01:05:01,700
相机摆放的位置
According to the placement of the camera...

675
01:05:01,851 --> 01:05:03,827
说明死者经常使用它
...the victim used it all the time.

676
01:05:03,978 --> 01:05:07,956
但是里面就是没有SD卡
But there's no SD card in it.Unless...

677
01:05:08,107 --> 01:05:10,125
除非 被人拿走啦
It was taken out.

678
01:05:10,276 --> 01:05:13,920
可我还是不明白 这跟咖啡馆有什么关系
I still don't know what it has to do with the coffee shop.

679
01:05:14,405 --> 01:05:17,841
死者这三个月来 常去的地方
For the past three months,the usual haunts of the victim...

680
01:05:17,992 --> 01:05:21,470
除了超市 就是这
...are the supermarket and the coffee shop.

681
01:05:21,621 --> 01:05:24,848
为什么要去这么远的地方喝咖啡
Why did he go all the way there to have coffee?

682
01:05:24,999 --> 01:05:27,267
咖啡好喝
Because the coffee there is good.

683
01:05:27,835 --> 01:05:31,271
最后一个线索 你去不去
This is the last clue.Are you coming or not?

684
01:05:32,131 --> 01:05:36,443
凶手已经嚣张到 来警察局挑衅了
The murderer is so arrogant that he provoked in the police office!

685
01:05:36,594 --> 01:05:40,280
你们这么多人都抓不到他
And you actually let him slip away!

686
01:05:40,431 --> 01:05:44,201
我要发动全曼谷的警察抓捕这个唐仁
I will order all the cops of Bangkok to get Tang Ren.

687
01:05:44,352 --> 01:05:46,953
三天 我给你们三天时间
Three days.I'll give you three days.

688
01:05:47,772 --> 01:05:53,919
抓不住唐仁 你们都去NANA摸屁股吧
If you can't get him by then,you can sell yourselves at Nana!

689
01:05:54,445 --> 01:05:56,963
见过这人没有
Have you seen this guy?

690
01:05:59,659 --> 01:06:02,094
这个人啊 之前经常来的
This guy used to come here all the time.

691
01:06:02,245 --> 01:06:06,932
坐在那个位置 最近不知道怎么了 就不来了
He sat there every time. But he hasn't shown up for a while.

692
01:06:07,417 --> 01:06:10,060
还有什么特别的 没什么特别的
Anything special about him?- Nothing special.

693
01:06:10,211 --> 01:06:14,731
他喜欢拿个破相机 对着外面 拍来拍去的
He often aimed his camera at the outside and took pictures.

694
01:06:20,304 --> 01:06:24,366
你好 两位SIR 咖啡还是茶 必须要喝吗
Hello. Sirs, coffee or tea?- Do we have to drink something?

695
01:06:24,559 --> 01:06:27,828
拜托 这是咖啡馆好吗 好 来杯咖啡啦
Come on, this is a coffee shop.- Fine, a coffee for me.

696
01:06:27,979 --> 01:06:32,916
一百株 谢谢
100 baht.- Thank you.

697
01:06:39,198 --> 01:06:42,759
就一破楼有什么好拍的
Why would anyone want to take pictures of a lousy building?

698
01:06:43,328 --> 01:06:46,263
他拍的就是这个破楼
The building was his target.

699
01:06:48,708 --> 01:06:51,518
我要查看这里的住户登记册
I want to check the household register here.

700
01:06:51,669 --> 01:06:53,603
不行
No, you can't.

701
01:07:03,890 --> 01:07:07,701
两位SIR 咖啡还是茶 我们刚才不是点过了吗
Sirs, coffee or tea?- I thought we ordered coffee.

702
01:07:07,852 --> 01:07:10,495
但是你们又出去了呀 我们又回来啦
But you left.- But we come back now.

703
01:07:10,646 --> 01:07:13,457
你们出去再回来也是要重新点的呀
You have to order again when you come back.

704
01:07:13,733 --> 01:07:15,459
我们就上了个厕所啊
We just went to the bathroom.

705
01:07:15,610 --> 01:07:17,127
第一 你们是一起去上的厕所
Firstly, you went to the bathroom at the same time.

706
01:07:17,278 --> 01:07:18,795
第二 你们上的不是我们家的厕所
Secondly,you didn't use our bathroom.

707
01:07:18,946 --> 01:07:21,798
第三 你们上厕所的时间未免也 太长了吧
Thirdly, it took you too long in the bathroom.

708
01:07:21,949 --> 01:07:24,468
来杯咖啡啦 一百株
A coffee for me.-100 baht.

709
01:07:26,829 --> 01:07:29,473
我要给你们点个差评啦 谢谢
I'll give a negative comment!- Thank you.

710
01:07:35,505 --> 01:07:37,856
这是什么意思
What does this mean?

711
01:07:38,883 --> 01:07:43,320
公 公帕 丁 沙丁
Gongpa Shading...

712
01:07:43,513 --> 01:07:47,491
公泰普萨提萨散 一所中学的名字
Gong Tai Pu Sa Ti Sa San.The name of a middle school.

713
01:07:54,440 --> 01:07:56,458
是颂帕失踪儿子的学校
Sompat's son studied there.

714
01:07:56,609 --> 01:07:58,710
两份资料里 唯一重合的信息
This is the only overlapping information in the two materials.

715
01:07:58,861 --> 01:08:02,005
算是突破口吗 最强大脑啊
Is it a breakthrough?You have an amazing mind.

716
01:08:02,156 --> 01:08:04,216
人肉相机 还自带辨识功能
You are a human camera and an automatic recognition machine.

717
01:08:04,367 --> 01:08:05,801
去看看谁在家
Let's see who they are.

718
01:08:23,761 --> 01:08:26,947
谁呀 我们是警察
Who is it?- The police.

719
01:08:27,098 --> 01:08:30,200
一会咋说 我自己来说啦
What should we say?- Leave it to me.

720
01:08:33,730 --> 01:08:36,248
中国人 对啊 你也是啊
Are you Chinese?- Yes, so are you.

721
01:08:36,399 --> 01:08:39,918
小妹妹 太巧了 看 我们是警察
What a coincidence.Look. We are with the police.

722
01:08:40,236 --> 01:08:43,130
可不可以问你几句话啦 嗯
Can we ask you a few questions?

723
01:08:46,159 --> 01:08:49,136
你叫什么名字啊 我叫思诺
What's your name?- I'm Snow.

724
01:08:50,997 --> 01:08:53,682
大人不在 爸爸上工了
Your parents are not home?- My dad has gone to work.

725
01:08:54,959 --> 01:08:57,853
你这么小也可以当警察啊
Aren't you too young to be a cop?

726
01:08:58,004 --> 01:09:00,605
他是我的助手啦
He is my assistant.

727
01:09:07,013 --> 01:09:11,533
小妹妹 这个人你认识吗 他是我隔壁班同学
Do you know him?- He is my schoolmate.

728
01:09:11,684 --> 01:09:14,202
好久都没有去学校了
He has been absent from school for a long time.

729
01:09:14,354 --> 01:09:16,538
大家都说他失踪了
Everybody says he has gone missing.

730
01:09:16,689 --> 01:09:19,249
你知道是什么原因吗
Do you know why?

731
01:09:20,568 --> 01:09:23,128
这个人认识吗
Do you know this guy?

732
01:09:25,531 --> 01:09:30,135
那你有没有感觉 最近有人在跟踪你呀 没有啊
Are you stalked by anyone lately?- No.

733
01:09:30,286 --> 01:09:33,638
那最近有没有什么怪事发生
Did anything weird happen to you lately?

734
01:09:33,790 --> 01:09:36,641
或者你遇到什么怪人呢
Did you run into any weirdos?

735
01:09:38,461 --> 01:09:41,521
你们 算吗
Do you guys count?

736
01:09:52,392 --> 01:09:55,744
你干嘛
What are you doing?

737
01:09:56,104 --> 01:10:01,416
你 真好看 谢谢
You are so pretty.- Thank you.

738
01:10:07,824 --> 01:10:10,675
年轻气盛啊
Youth.

739
01:10:10,910 --> 01:10:13,178
有没有发现什么
Have you got anything?

740
01:10:13,329 --> 01:10:15,555
你是不是对人家小妞有意思啊
You have a crush on her,don't you?

741
01:10:15,707 --> 01:10:18,934
你胡说什么呢你 一看你就对人家小妞有意思啦
What are you talking about?- It's so obvious.

742
01:10:20,169 --> 01:10:21,937
又来
Again!

743
01:10:22,672 --> 01:10:25,315
我们老板有请
Our boss wants to see you.

744
01:10:46,738 --> 01:10:48,714
老板好啊
Nice to meet you.

745
01:10:48,865 --> 01:10:54,386
知道你们偷的黄金 是谁的吗 闫先生的
Do you know who is the owner of the stolen gold? Mr. Yan.

746
01:10:59,042 --> 01:11:02,853
闫先生 那黄金不是我们偷的啊
Mr. Yan, we didn't steal the gold.

747
01:11:08,718 --> 01:11:11,403
闫先生 你的黄金不是我们偷的啊
Mr. Yan, we didn't steal the gold.

748
01:11:11,554 --> 01:11:14,114
警察说是你们
The police told me it was you.

749
01:11:14,265 --> 01:11:17,284
警察也经常搞错啊
The police makes mistakes all the time.

750
01:11:17,435 --> 01:11:19,911
我知道偷你黄金的五个人是谁了
I know the five guys who stole your gold.

751
01:11:20,730 --> 01:11:24,708
谁 我说出来 你就把我们放啦
Who are they?- Let us go after I tell you.

752
01:11:24,859 --> 01:11:27,252
跟我讨价还价 不 不 不
Are you bargaining with me?- No, no, no.

753
01:11:27,403 --> 01:11:30,213
死的人是颂帕 黄兰登的助手托尼
The victim Sompat,Huang Landeng's assistant Tony...

754
01:11:30,365 --> 01:11:32,340
一个东北人 还有一个越南人
...a northeasterner,a Vietnamese...

755
01:11:32,492 --> 01:11:37,137
还有一个叫金刚的 胖吧拉唧的 傻大个子
...and a fat, big guy,called King Kong.

756
01:11:37,288 --> 01:11:38,764
我怎么知道你说的是真的
How do I know if you are telling the truth?

757
01:11:38,915 --> 01:11:42,768
他可以证明啊 我可以证明
He can prove it.- I can prove it.

758
01:11:47,340 --> 01:11:50,650
你们这是在搞笑是不是
Are you kidding me?

759
01:11:51,803 --> 01:11:54,362
我也可以证明
I can prove it, too.

760
01:11:57,475 --> 01:12:00,369
阿香 闫先生
Xiang.- Mr. Yan.

761
01:12:00,520 --> 01:12:02,454
那三个人我见过
I met those three guys.

762
01:12:02,605 --> 01:12:05,957
而且我知道 是坤泰帮他们找了跑路的船
And I know that Kon Tai helped him get the boat to leave here.

763
01:12:06,109 --> 01:12:08,960
如果黄金在他们手里 他们是不会回来的
If they have the gold,they wouldn't have stayed.

764
01:12:09,112 --> 01:12:10,754
阿香 闭嘴
Xiang.- Shut up.

765
01:12:10,905 --> 01:12:13,715
闫先生 请你相信阿香
Mr. Yan, please believe me.

766
01:12:13,866 --> 01:12:18,053
就算不是你们偷的 但是黄金终归是你从颂帕那给运走的
Even if you didn't steal it, you moved it from Sompat's Workshop.

767
01:12:18,204 --> 01:12:20,305
可我完全是不知情啊
I knew nothing about it.

768
01:12:20,456 --> 01:12:23,767
看在阿香的面子上 我给你十天的时间找回黄金
For Xiang's sake, I'll give you ten days to find the gold.

769
01:12:23,918 --> 01:12:28,397
十天之内 我保证不会难为你们
I won't touch you within ten days.

770
01:12:28,548 --> 01:12:31,733
十天之后 会把你扔到湄南河去
Find it in time, or I will throw you into the Menam River...

771
01:12:31,884 --> 01:12:33,819
喂鳄鱼
...to feed the crocodiles.

772
01:12:33,970 --> 01:12:36,279
还不谢谢闫先生 十天
Thank Mr. Yan for that.- Ten days?

773
01:12:36,431 --> 01:12:38,448
给二十天吧 七天
How about twenty days?- Seven days.

774
01:12:38,599 --> 01:12:40,158
半个月 半个月好啦
Half a month.Half a month will do.

775
01:12:40,309 --> 01:12:42,953
五天 行 行 好 五天就五天
Five days.- Fine, fine. Five days.

776
01:12:43,104 --> 01:12:45,205
不能再减了 再减就成负的了
It can't be less than that.

777
01:12:47,984 --> 01:12:50,544
你看行吗
What do you think?

778
01:12:50,695 --> 01:12:52,421
好 OK 成交
Okay, it's a deal.

779
01:12:52,572 --> 01:12:57,509
三天 就三天
Three days. Just three days.

780
01:12:57,660 --> 01:12:58,221
你疯啦
Are you out of your mind?

781
01:13:02,165 --> 01:13:04,558
好 就三天
All right, three days.

782
01:13:04,709 --> 01:13:07,227
我们一言为定 你就害死我吧
I'll give you three days.- You are going to get me killed.

783
01:13:07,378 --> 01:13:08,895
我给你三天的时间 五天我就赶不上回家飞机了
I don't have that much time before I go home.

784
01:13:09,047 --> 01:13:13,692
有任何需要我帮忙 尽管开口
Just let me know if you need any help.

785
01:13:13,843 --> 01:13:16,529
三天一过 我保证
Find the gold in time,or I promise that...

786
01:13:16,680 --> 01:13:17,406
你会去见鳄鱼
...you will be fed to the crocodiles.

787
01:13:19,557 --> 01:13:21,783
疯了 你一定是疯了
Crazy. You must be crazy.

788
01:13:21,934 --> 01:13:23,452
五天不要 要三天
You asked for three days instead of five.

789
01:13:23,603 --> 01:13:25,454
三天我们去哪里找黄金啊
How can we find the gold in three days?

790
01:13:25,605 --> 01:13:27,497
你知道闫先生是谁吗
Do you know who Mr. Yan is?

791
01:13:27,648 --> 01:13:30,792
唐人街金铺一大半都是他开的啦
Most of the gold shops in Chinatown are owned by him.

792
01:13:30,943 --> 01:13:33,086
出租车 大市场 华人超市 KTV
The taxi company, floating market,Chinese market and KTV club...

793
01:13:33,237 --> 01:13:35,422
那都是他开的啦
...are all owned by him.

794
01:13:35,573 --> 01:13:38,925
全泰国黑白两道 都没人敢惹他
The officials or the gangsters,nobody wants to mess with him.

795
01:13:39,077 --> 01:13:40,677
就连军方都得给他面子
Even the military shows him respect.

796
01:13:40,828 --> 01:13:44,639
他说让我们喂鳄鱼 就会把我们喂鳄鱼啦
If he said we would be fed to the crocodiles, we would.

797
01:13:44,791 --> 01:13:49,269
他说的是你 不是你们
He meant you, not us.

798
01:13:50,880 --> 01:13:54,733
你什么意思 这时候分你我啦
What are you talking about?You want to be done with me now?

799
01:13:54,884 --> 01:13:58,111
我们不是搭档吗 唐人街神探吗
Aren't we partners?The detectives of Chinatown?

800
01:13:58,262 --> 01:14:02,032
我还是你舅舅呢 你有没有点人性
And I'm your uncle, too.You are inhumane!

801
01:14:02,183 --> 01:14:04,868
现在去哪里啊 去那女孩学校看看
Where are we going now?- To the girl's school.

802
01:14:05,019 --> 01:14:08,288
现在你还去泡妞
You are going to pick up girls now?

803
01:14:08,439 --> 01:14:10,832
大哥 我们只有三天
We only have three days.

804
01:14:10,983 --> 01:14:12,751
三天就喂鳄鱼了
Then we will be fed to the crocodiles.

805
01:14:12,902 --> 01:14:15,921
只有把凶杀案破了 才能找回黄金
Only after we solve the murder can we find the gold.

806
01:14:16,072 --> 01:14:21,927
你破个屁 你有一点点线索吗 这几天我一直都在陪你玩
Nonsense! Do you have any clues?I have been with you these days.

807
01:14:22,078 --> 01:14:23,929
你有个毛线索啊
I don't think you have gotten anything.

808
01:14:24,080 --> 01:14:25,806
凶手在哪里呢
Where is the murderer?

809
01:14:25,957 --> 01:14:30,602
你连人家什么时候进去杀人 什么时候出来你都不知道
You don't even know when he went in and out.

810
01:14:30,753 --> 01:14:34,564
你别以为你多看了几本侦探小说 就真把自己当神探了吗
You think you are a real detective because you read a few fictions?

811
01:14:35,675 --> 01:14:39,111
谁陪谁玩啊 我是来放假的
You're wrong.I'm on vacation here.

812
01:14:39,262 --> 01:14:44,783
结果呢 大皇宫呢
And? I haven't gone to the Grand Palace.

813
01:14:44,934 --> 01:14:47,953
我这几天 我吃过饭 睡过觉吗
I haven't eaten or slept for the last few days.

814
01:14:49,022 --> 01:14:53,917
反正还剩三天
Anyway, there are three days left.

815
01:14:54,652 --> 01:14:58,880
我知道了 三天一到 你就打飞的回国了
I know. Three days later,you will fly home...

816
01:14:59,032 --> 01:15:01,508
扔下我去喂鳄鱼 对不对
...and leave me here for the crocodiles, won't you?

817
01:15:01,659 --> 01:15:03,802
对
Yes.

818
01:15:03,953 --> 01:15:06,346
我们是搭档 唐人街神探
Partners,the detectives of Chinatown.

819
01:15:06,497 --> 01:15:09,224
都是骗我的 对不对 对
They are all lies, aren't they?- Yes.

820
01:15:09,375 --> 01:15:14,229
我可是你舅舅啊 表的
I am your uncle.- No, just a distant uncle.

821
01:15:14,380 --> 01:15:16,648
我没你这么LOW的舅舅
I don't have a loser uncle like you.

822
01:15:16,799 --> 01:15:21,737
你是小唐 我是老秦
You are Tang, and I'm Qin.

823
01:15:23,097 --> 01:15:28,118
你别以为我离开你个小毛孩子 我就找不到黄金 破不了案
You think I can't find the gold and solve the case without you?

824
01:15:28,269 --> 01:15:30,412
我还不当你这个保姆了呢
I don't want to be your babysitter anymore.

825
01:15:30,563 --> 01:15:34,374
你以为我愿意陪你这个脑残啊
You think I want to be with a moron like you?

826
01:15:34,525 --> 01:15:38,545
散伙 散伙就散伙 散伙
Break up!- Fine. Break up!

827
01:16:03,888 --> 01:16:06,615
闫先生要见你
Mr. Yan wants to see you.

828
01:16:22,990 --> 01:16:26,259
大叔呢 没和你一起来
Where is your uncle?He is not with you?

829
01:16:26,411 --> 01:16:29,638
我 家里没人 走吧
I...- Nobody's home. Let's go.

830
01:16:51,602 --> 01:16:54,162
借个火
Give me a light.

831
01:17:47,992 --> 01:17:51,178
你怎么又是一个人在家
Why are you alone at home again?

832
01:17:51,954 --> 01:17:54,347
我爸妈死于一场车祸
My parents died in a car accident.

833
01:17:54,499 --> 01:17:56,850
养父从孤儿院里把我带回来
My stepfather adopted me from the orphanage.

834
01:17:57,001 --> 01:17:59,978
他在上工
He has gone to work.

835
01:18:00,129 --> 01:18:03,356
你呢 你父母呢
What about your parents?

836
01:18:03,508 --> 01:18:07,110
我妈很早以前就去世了
My mother passed away a long time ago.

837
01:18:07,261 --> 01:18:10,906
那你爸爸呢 在牢里
What about your dad?- He is in prison.

838
01:18:11,057 --> 01:18:16,995
他犯了什么罪啊  我也不太清楚
What did he do?- I don't know.

839
01:18:17,146 --> 01:18:19,623
那他是坏人吗
Is he a bad guy?

840
01:18:19,774 --> 01:18:24,419
好 坏 看怎么理解了
Good or bad, it depends.

841
01:18:24,570 --> 01:18:27,422
你说话一直这样吗
Do you always talk like this?

842
01:18:27,573 --> 01:18:30,092
我之前就不太说话
I barely talked when I was younger.

843
01:18:30,243 --> 01:18:32,844
现在好多了
I'm better now.

844
01:18:35,248 --> 01:18:37,808
你们为什么要冒充警察
Why did you pose as police?

845
01:18:38,001 --> 01:18:42,479
谁说的 你不是很上镜
Who told you that?- You are not so photogenic.

846
01:18:42,922 --> 01:18:47,484
那你为什么还放我进来 我觉得 你不是坏人
So why did you invite me in?- I don't think you are a bad guy.

847
01:18:47,635 --> 01:18:52,656
可是你们为什么要来找我 丹的爸爸 他一直在跟踪你
But why did you come to me?- Dan's father was stalking you.

848
01:18:52,807 --> 01:18:56,785
是吗 为什么啊 我也想知道
Did he? Why?- I want to know that, too.

849
01:18:58,271 --> 01:19:01,456
今天物理老师留了一个很奇怪的作业
Our physics teacher left us a funny assignment today.

850
01:19:02,150 --> 01:19:05,293
如何把一张纸给立起来
To make a piece of paper stand.

851
01:19:15,079 --> 01:19:18,640
这也太简单了 是太简单了
It can't be so simple.- Yes, you are right.

852
01:19:24,714 --> 01:19:26,606
爸爸
Dad.

853
01:19:26,758 --> 01:19:30,402
他是谁 同学
Who is he?- My classmate.

854
01:20:39,998 --> 01:20:42,891
那我先走了
I have to go.

855
01:21:01,310 --> 01:21:03,328
我送你
I'll see you out.

856
01:21:13,448 --> 01:21:18,093
黄兰登 你别追了
Huang Landeng, stop chasing me.

857
01:21:18,244 --> 01:21:21,388
你不跑 我就不追了
Only if you stop running.

858
01:21:21,539 --> 01:21:24,349
你不追 我就不跑了
I will, as soon as you stop.

859
01:21:24,500 --> 01:21:27,227
你不跑 我就不追了
Not before you stop.

860
01:21:53,321 --> 01:21:57,382
你跑啊 跑死我了
Go ahead. I'm exhausted.

861
01:22:00,578 --> 01:22:03,555
你别逼我 你要再逼我
Don't push me.If you push me again...

862
01:22:03,706 --> 01:22:07,017
我就跳下去 你跳啊
...I'll jump.- Go ahead, jump!

863
01:22:21,140 --> 01:22:25,160
天灵灵 地灵灵 天都帮不了你
God bless me.- Even God can't help you now.

864
01:22:25,311 --> 01:22:31,208
唐仁 盗窃黄金 谋杀颂帕
Tang Ren, you stole the gold and murdered Sompat.

865
01:22:31,401 --> 01:22:34,669
我要逮捕你
You are under arrest.

866
01:22:46,332 --> 01:22:50,685
再见 唐仁 你给我回来
Hello.- Tang Ren, come back here!

867
01:23:10,440 --> 01:23:13,959
我猜你就在这里啦
I knew you'd be here.

868
01:23:45,767 --> 01:23:47,743
我知道了
I know.

869
01:23:47,894 --> 01:23:51,455
你说 那些录像里 除了我没有其他人进出 对不对
The video footages showed that there was nobodygoing in or out but me, right?

870
01:23:52,606 --> 01:23:52,915
对
Right.

871
01:23:53,067 --> 01:23:56,586
你和警察确定 这里没有其它入口 对不对
You and the police are sure there's no other entrance, right?

872
01:23:57,820 --> 01:24:04,009
对 颂帕 是被这降魔杵打死的
Yes.- Sompat was killed by the vajra.

873
01:24:05,495 --> 01:24:08,555
他会不会 是他做了太多坏事
Is it possible that he did too many evils...

874
01:24:10,106 --> 01:24:11,708
金刚显灵
...and the vajra made its power felt?

875
01:24:11,959 --> 01:24:13,269
金刚来了
The vajra is here!

876
01:24:19,509 --> 01:24:23,111
这么恐怖的事你还笑得出来
How can you laugh at such a creepy thing?

877
01:24:24,555 --> 01:24:27,657
监视器内容 七天会自动覆盖
The footages are automatically overwritten every seven days.

878
01:24:27,809 --> 01:24:30,869
所以呢
So?

879
01:24:31,020 --> 01:24:33,455
我不相信什么鬼神
I don't believe in supernatural beings.

880
01:24:33,606 --> 01:24:37,084
唯一的解释 凶手
The only explanation is that the murderer...

881
01:24:37,235 --> 01:24:39,461
一周前就藏在这儿了
...had been hiding here a week before.

882
01:24:39,612 --> 01:24:43,632
什么 一周前就藏在这儿啦 这怎么可能呢
What? Hiding here a week before?How is that possible?

883
01:24:44,701 --> 01:24:48,136
歌野晶午的《求道者密室》
In Shogo Utano's "The Secret Chamber of the Seeker"...

884
01:24:48,287 --> 01:24:51,098
凶手为了杀人 躲在天井里
...the murderer hid in the courtyard for a month...

885
01:24:51,249 --> 01:24:54,643
一个月
...to kill someone.

886
01:24:55,128 --> 01:24:58,397
大哥 那是小说嘛
That's fictional.

887
01:24:58,548 --> 01:25:00,690
福尔摩斯说过
Sherlock Holmes said...

888
01:25:00,842 --> 01:25:02,943
排除所有不可能
...when you have eliminated all which is impossible...

889
01:25:03,094 --> 01:25:07,030
剩下那个多不可思议
...then whatever remains,however improbable...

890
01:25:08,141 --> 01:25:10,659
都是事实真相
...must be the truth.

891
01:25:13,021 --> 01:25:16,456
那他藏在哪里呢 不会被发现吗
So where did he hide?He'd be discovered, wouldn't he?

892
01:25:16,649 --> 01:25:19,376
你还记得丹的房间吗
Do you remember Dan's room?

893
01:25:21,362 --> 01:25:25,799
颂帕不会经常进自己死儿子的房间
Sompat didn't often go to the room of his dead son.

894
01:25:27,243 --> 01:25:29,886
他就躲在丹的床底下
So the murderer hid under Dan's bed.

895
01:25:30,038 --> 01:25:32,931
那个脚印 是他不小心留下的
He left that footprint by accident.

896
01:25:33,082 --> 01:25:35,350
对 可他每天吃什么呢
Yes.- But what did he eat every day?

897
01:25:35,501 --> 01:25:37,894
他的大小便怎么办呢
And what if he wanted to go the bathroom?

898
01:25:38,087 --> 01:25:40,647
颂帕常去咖啡馆 你还记得吧
Sompat often went to the coffee shop, remember?

899
01:25:40,798 --> 01:25:42,858
这个人啊 之前经常来这
This guy used to come here all the time.

900
01:25:43,009 --> 01:25:48,113
自己家里 一直藏着一个 想杀死自己的人
A man who wants to kill you has been hiding in your home.

901
01:25:48,264 --> 01:25:50,282
这想想太恐怖了
It's so creepy just to think of it.

902
01:25:50,433 --> 01:25:52,993
现在我们案件重演
Now let's re-enact the murder.

903
01:25:53,144 --> 01:25:54,911
有这个必要吗
Is it necessary?

904
01:25:55,063 --> 01:25:59,833
要破解罪恶 就必须接近它 甚至成为它
To solve the crime, you have to approach it, or even be it.

905
01:25:59,984 --> 01:26:03,045
我演你 你演颂帕
I'll play you,and you'll play Sompat.

906
01:26:10,286 --> 01:26:12,637
老板 取货
Sir, I'm here for a pick up.

907
01:26:12,830 --> 01:26:15,098
不对 怎么了
No.- What?

908
01:26:15,249 --> 01:26:18,894
我说这话时没结巴 你演你
I didn't stutter.- Fine, you play yourself.

909
01:26:19,045 --> 01:26:21,438
我演颂帕
I'll play Sompat.

910
01:26:21,923 --> 01:26:25,525
记住 别错过任何 细节
Remember, don't miss any details.

911
01:26:34,852 --> 01:26:37,120
取货
I'm here for a pick up.

912
01:26:43,069 --> 01:26:45,045
坐
Sit.

913
01:26:46,989 --> 01:26:49,424
停
Stop.

914
01:26:51,244 --> 01:26:55,222
你的指纹 继续吗
Your finger prints.- Go on?

915
01:26:57,542 --> 01:26:59,267
继续
Go on.

916
01:27:09,971 --> 01:27:12,739
停 又停
Stop.- Again?

917
01:27:12,890 --> 01:27:18,286
你确定 他是先给你钱 再给你单子的
Are you sure he paid you before he handed you the note?

918
01:27:23,943 --> 01:27:29,005
对啊 怎么了 他自始至终只跟你说了一个坐
Yes. Why?- All he said to you was "sit"?

919
01:27:29,157 --> 01:27:34,845
没错啊 好 继续
Yes.- Okay. Go on.

920
01:27:58,519 --> 01:28:01,204
停 我就知道啦
Stop.- I knew it.

921
01:28:01,356 --> 01:28:04,207
你走的时候 没看见颂帕
When you left,you didn't see Sompat?

922
01:28:04,359 --> 01:28:07,669
他在工作室里 我只看到他的影子啦
He was in his studio,and all I saw was his silhouette.

923
01:28:08,780 --> 01:28:14,926
影子
His silhouette.

924
01:28:31,594 --> 01:28:35,072
你那天看到的 是不是这样的颂帕
The Sompat you saw that day was like this, wasn't he?

925
01:28:40,353 --> 01:28:43,413
对 对 对 就是这个样子
Yes, exactly.

926
01:28:48,111 --> 01:28:49,961
到底怎么回事 凶手在哪里呢
What's going on?Where is the murderer?

927
01:28:50,113 --> 01:28:52,005
凶手就在你眼前 你是凶手
He is right beneath your eyes.- You are the murderer?

928
01:28:52,156 --> 01:28:54,800
对 我是凶手 别闹了你
Yes, I am the murderer.- Stop it!

929
01:28:54,951 --> 01:28:57,803
不是 我演的这个是凶手
No. The man I play is the murderer.

930
01:28:57,996 --> 01:29:00,680
你演的是颂帕 颂帕杀死了自己
You play Sompat.You mean Sompat killed himself?

931
01:29:00,832 --> 01:29:04,184
我知道了 他是自杀
I know. He committed suicide.

932
01:29:04,335 --> 01:29:08,105
神探大哥 你自己砸碎自己后脑勺试试
Detective, try to smash the back of your own head.

933
01:29:09,215 --> 01:29:11,108
到底怎么回事吗
So what the heck happened?

934
01:29:11,259 --> 01:29:15,153
你没看清他的脸 对不对 对啊 那灯光太暗了嘛
You didn't see his face clearly.- The light was too dim.

935
01:29:17,473 --> 01:29:20,617
那天是不是这个样子 对啊 就是这个样子啦
Was it like this that day?- Yes, exactly like this.

936
01:29:20,768 --> 01:29:22,536
那是他不想让你看清
He didn't want you to see him clearly...

937
01:29:22,729 --> 01:29:24,705
因为 他根本就不是颂帕
...because he was not Sompat.

938
01:29:24,856 --> 01:29:26,957
 难道他是 凶手
He was...- The murderer.

939
01:29:27,108 --> 01:29:28,875
凶手来啦
The murderer is here!- Right.

940
01:30:00,141 --> 01:30:03,076
你没事吧 我没事
Are you okay?- I'm fine.

941
01:30:03,227 --> 01:30:06,121
他是谁呀 他要杀我们
Who is he?- He wants to kill us.

942
01:30:06,314 --> 01:30:09,082
只能证明 证明什么
It means...- What?

943
01:30:10,026 --> 01:30:12,878
我们对了 我们对了
We are right.- We are right?

944
01:30:16,032 --> 01:30:20,385
不好 快跑啊
Oh, no!- Run!

945
01:30:37,095 --> 01:30:38,031
小唐
Tang!

946
01:30:38,231 --> 01:30:39,031
小唐
Tang!

947
01:30:39,931 --> 01:30:40,831
小唐
Tang!

948
01:30:43,601 --> 01:30:46,453
小唐
Tang!

949
01:30:49,357 --> 01:30:50,708
老秦 小唐
Qin!- Tang!

950
01:30:51,000 --> 01:30:51,700
老秦
Qin!

951
01:30:51,859 --> 01:30:55,046
小唐 小唐 我在这呢
Tang,Tang, I'm here!

952
01:30:57,240 --> 01:30:58,392
老秦
Qin!

953
01:30:58,892 --> 01:31:00,292
老秦
Qin!

954
01:31:10,211 --> 01:31:15,065
帮帮忙 帮帮忙 大哥 快点 快点啊
Come on, help us.Come on, come on.

955
01:31:25,476 --> 01:31:27,369
不要命了吗
Do you want to live?

956
01:31:28,354 --> 01:31:31,498
走 一 二 三
Let's go! One, two, three.

957
01:31:41,826 --> 01:31:44,928
你要这个东西干什么
What do you want this for?

958
01:31:45,705 --> 01:31:48,181
这是证据
This is evidence.

959
01:31:51,419 --> 01:31:54,312
查案重要 还是活着重要啊
Which is more important,your life or solving the case?

960
01:31:55,590 --> 01:31:57,816
都重要
They are both important.

961
01:32:03,890 --> 01:32:05,574
走啦
Let's go.

962
01:32:30,375 --> 01:32:35,353
闫先生已经知道我底细啦 泰国我是待不下去了
Mr. Yan has blown my cover.I can't stay in Thailand anymore.

963
01:32:35,505 --> 01:32:38,106
你可以去澳洲啊 那边阳光好
You can go to Australia.There's great sunshine...

964
01:32:38,257 --> 01:32:40,233
海鲜也很棒啊 是哦
...and delicious seafood.- Really?

965
01:32:40,385 --> 01:32:42,652
对呀 你们耍我啊
Yes.- Are you kidding me?

966
01:32:44,263 --> 01:32:46,740
很简单 我数三声
It's simple. I'll count to three.

967
01:32:46,891 --> 01:32:51,453
告诉我黄金在哪里 不然我一枪打死她
And you tell me where the gold is.Or I'll shoot her.

968
01:32:51,604 --> 01:32:53,580
一 我们真的不知道啊
One.- We really don't know.

969
01:32:53,731 --> 01:32:55,332
你真的不知道吗 我真的不知道啊
Really?- I really don't know!

970
01:32:55,483 --> 01:32:57,209
你真的不知道吗 真的不知道啊
Really?- Really!

971
01:32:57,443 --> 01:33:01,755
大哥
My friend.

972
01:33:08,663 --> 01:33:11,473
可怜可怜我吧 我真的很惨的
Have some pity on me.

973
01:33:12,333 --> 01:33:16,728
我们几个人 策划了半年多
We spent over six months planning for this.

974
01:33:16,879 --> 01:33:18,688
好不容易黄金到手了 现在什么都没了
And when we finally got the gold,it was gone.

975
01:33:21,300 --> 01:33:23,193
现在泰国我 待不下去了
Now I can't stay in Thailand anymore.

976
01:33:23,344 --> 01:33:25,153
我还有妈妈要照顾  我只能跑路
I still have to provide for my mother. I have to leave here.

977
01:33:25,304 --> 01:33:26,822
很惨的
I am in misery.

978
01:33:26,973 --> 01:33:29,991
把枪放下 你告诉他
Put the gun down.- You tell him.

979
01:33:30,143 --> 01:33:32,285
我
Me?

980
01:33:34,564 --> 01:33:38,834
我 哦 对 他本来就结巴
I...- Well, he is a stutterer.

981
01:33:38,985 --> 01:33:40,919
这一紧张就更结巴啦
And even more so when he is nervous.

982
01:33:41,070 --> 01:33:43,255
不着急 慢慢来 我等你 大把时间啊
Take it easy. I can wait.I have a lot of time.

983
01:33:43,406 --> 01:33:45,340
二 别
Two.- Don't!

984
01:33:45,491 --> 01:33:48,009
我 我知道了
I...- I know!

985
01:33:48,161 --> 01:33:51,304
唱歌就不结巴 对 你把想说的都唱出来呀
You won't stutter if you sing.You can sing it out.

986
01:33:51,456 --> 01:33:53,765
我不会唱 唱歌有什么难的
I can't sing.- What's so difficult about that?

987
01:33:53,916 --> 01:33:56,101
我唱一句 你唱一句
Sing along with me.

988
01:33:56,252 --> 01:34:01,064
时光一逝永不回
Time is gone with the wind.

989
01:34:01,215 --> 01:34:03,358
预备 唱
Ready? Sing!

990
01:34:03,801 --> 01:34:09,072
时光一逝 停 停 停
Time is gone...- Stop, stop, stop.

991
01:34:09,223 --> 01:34:11,700
跑调了 不对 你唱得不对
You are out of tune.You're singing it wrong.

992
01:34:11,851 --> 01:34:15,495
嗦啦嗦咪 啦咪啦哆啦哆
So la so mi. La mi la do la do.

993
01:34:15,646 --> 01:34:21,501
时光一逝 啦咪啦哆啦哆
Time is gone...- La mi la do la do.

994
01:34:21,652 --> 01:34:25,464
永不回 对 对 对 好很多了
With the wind.- It sounds better now.

995
01:34:25,615 --> 01:34:30,218
你那个光唱得特别好 你再把那个回再拉得长一点
Your "time" sounds very well.You have to keep "wind" longer.

996
01:34:30,370 --> 01:34:32,304
回 拉长一点儿啦
Wind. Keep it longer.

997
01:34:32,455 --> 01:34:36,600
永不回 回
Gone with the wind.- Wind.

998
01:34:36,793 --> 01:34:44,608
你们觉得我很二吗 我是不是很二 好啊 我二 OK 给你们最后一个机会
Do you think I'm dumb? Am I dumb?This is your last chance.

999
01:34:44,759 --> 01:34:47,110
不要 二点八
No!- Two and a half.

1000
01:34:47,261 --> 01:34:49,863
你快告诉他 别吵 我 我 我
Just tell him!- I...

1001
01:34:50,014 --> 01:34:53,492
你这个小结巴 说 关键时刻你就结巴 怪不得你考不上大学
You are such a loser. No wonder you can't get into college.

1002
01:34:53,643 --> 01:34:55,827
大学就不能要你这个小结巴
No college will admit a little stutterer like you.

1003
01:34:56,270 --> 01:34:58,705
那也比你好 你还侦探呢
I'm better than you.You think you are a detective.

1004
01:34:59,107 --> 01:35:01,583
你就是个老流氓 你敢骂我
You are actually an old hooligan.- How dare you call me that?

1005
01:35:01,734 --> 01:35:03,794
我骂你怎么了 老流氓
So what? You old hooligan!- You little stutterer!

1006
01:35:03,945 --> 01:35:05,921
你个小结巴 你个老流氓
You old hooligan!- You little stutterer!

1007
01:35:06,072 --> 01:35:07,798
你个小结巴 你个老流氓
You old hooligan!- I'm the point.

1008
01:35:07,949 --> 01:35:10,634
你个老结巴 重点是我 小流氓
You old stutterer!- Little hooligan!

1009
01:35:34,809 --> 01:35:37,327
阿香 你没事吧 我没事
Xiang, are you okay?- I'm okay.

1010
01:35:50,074 --> 01:35:52,175
阿香 阿香
Xiang!Xiang!

1011
01:35:52,368 --> 01:35:54,469
滴滴打车 送医院啊
Use DiDi Taxi to take her to the hospital.

1012
01:35:54,620 --> 01:35:56,680
还萨瓦迪卡呢 叫救护车
What are you talking about?Call the ambulance!

1013
01:35:58,666 --> 01:36:00,517
阿香
Xiang!

1014
01:36:00,752 --> 01:36:02,602
请您止步
Please stop here.

1015
01:36:02,754 --> 01:36:04,396
走啊 往哪走啊
Let's go!- Where to?

1016
01:36:04,547 --> 01:36:07,149
警察 来就来
The police is here!- I don't care!

1017
01:36:07,300 --> 01:36:10,110
大不了被抓走啊
They can arrest me here.

1018
01:36:13,306 --> 01:36:16,408
阿香 原来这么爱我
Xiang, now I know how much you love me.

1019
01:36:16,559 --> 01:36:18,577
肯为我挡枪
You are willing to take a bullet for me.

1020
01:36:18,728 --> 01:36:23,665
我怎么能辜负她呢 你想多了吧
How can I let her down?- You think too much.

1021
01:36:23,816 --> 01:36:29,755
等她好了 我要跟她生孩子 生很多很多孩子
When she gets well, I'll have kids with her. A lot of kids.

1022
01:36:29,906 --> 01:36:32,591
很多很多孩子
A lot of kids.

1023
01:36:45,004 --> 01:36:48,857
看我干什么
Why are you looking at me?

1024
01:36:49,008 --> 01:36:51,693
谢谢你救了我
Thanks for saving me.

1025
01:36:53,429 --> 01:36:55,363
别怪我拖累你就好啦 好好的假期
I hope you don't blame me for dragging you down.

1026
01:36:55,515 --> 01:36:59,910
怎么变成这个样子
Your vacation turns out like this.

1027
01:37:01,437 --> 01:37:04,748
你为什么来泰国
Why did you come to Thailand?

1028
01:37:04,899 --> 01:37:09,669
有哪个人 在国内混得舒坦 愿意出来呢
Anyone who has a good life at home won't go to another country.

1029
01:37:10,905 --> 01:37:15,425
留下有留下的原因 出来有出来的理由啦
We all have reasons to go abroad and stay.

1030
01:37:19,954 --> 01:37:20,947
误会了
It's not like that.

1031
01:37:21,147 --> 01:37:21,600
大哥
Eldest brother.

1032
01:37:22,047 --> 01:37:22,800
误会了
It's not like that.

1033
01:37:23,498 --> 01:37:26,601
很快整个镇子 都知道了这件丑事
In no time, the whole town knew about the scandal.

1034
01:37:27,836 --> 01:37:32,231
那时候 我才明白 你打算用什么料补呢
I finally realise that...- What would you like me to use?

1035
01:37:32,465 --> 01:37:36,110
这世上 比所有人瞧不起你还难受的滋味
Being pitied by everyone is more miserable than...

1036
01:37:36,261 --> 01:37:39,696
就是让所有人同情你
...being despised by them.

1037
01:37:40,473 --> 01:37:43,701
这么久了 你不想回去吗
It's been a long time.Don't you want to go home?

1038
01:37:43,852 --> 01:37:48,831
外面千好万好 都不如家好
There is no place like home.

1039
01:37:48,982 --> 01:37:51,542
可是回去又能干什么呢
But what can I do,even if I go back?

1040
01:37:51,693 --> 01:37:54,169
牛皮都已经吹出去了
I have been bragging aboutmy life here.

1041
01:37:54,320 --> 01:37:58,340
人家都以为你在外面混得风生水起
They all think I have a successful career.

1042
01:37:58,491 --> 01:38:04,221
其实 牙掉了 咽肚里
But I have to bear my own cross.

1043
01:38:04,414 --> 01:38:07,808
苦只有自己知道
And nobody knows my bitterness.

1044
01:38:07,959 --> 01:38:15,274
那些在外面 漂着不回家的人 都有自己的难处
Anybody who stay away from home have their own problems.

1045
01:38:17,260 --> 01:38:20,612
你呢 这么聪明
What about you? You are so smart.

1046
01:38:20,764 --> 01:38:25,159
警校不要你 那可是他们很大的损失呀
It's the police college's loss for rejecting you.

1047
01:38:27,896 --> 01:38:32,041
秦风同学 你为什么要报考刑警学院
Qin Feng, why do you want to get into the Criminal Police College?

1048
01:38:34,235 --> 01:38:37,588
这个问题很难回答吗
Is it so hard to answer?

1049
01:38:37,739 --> 01:38:42,968
我 不想说假话 我们也不想听假话呀
I don't want to lie to you.- We don't want you to lie.

1050
01:38:43,953 --> 01:38:48,182
我想完成一次 完美的犯罪
I want to commit a perfect crime.

1051
01:38:48,416 --> 01:38:51,643
啊 你是这么说
What? You actually said that?

1052
01:38:52,629 --> 01:38:54,563
你还真是个怪胎
You are really a freak.

1053
01:38:54,714 --> 01:38:56,815
看了这么多书和电影
You read all the books and watch all the movies...

1054
01:38:56,966 --> 01:38:59,610
不为破案 为犯罪
...not to solve crimes,but to commit one?

1055
01:39:12,607 --> 01:39:16,543
和你那 一直在狱里的老爸有关系
Does it have something to do with your dad in prison?

1056
01:39:18,238 --> 01:39:22,132
下回告诉你 下回 哪个下回
I'll tell you next time.- Next time? When is that?

1057
01:39:25,286 --> 01:39:27,721
没有生命危险
She's out of danger.

1058
01:39:31,835 --> 01:39:34,603
没事啦
She is fine.

1059
01:39:37,465 --> 01:39:39,400
这下跑不掉啦
We can't run away this time.

1060
01:39:39,551 --> 01:39:42,653
案子不是推理得差不多了吗 要不我们投降吧
The case is almost solved.How about we surrender?

1061
01:39:42,804 --> 01:39:44,655
不行 还差一点儿
No, I need the last piece of the puzzle.

1062
01:39:44,806 --> 01:39:46,490
还跑 跑
We have to run again?- Yes.

1063
01:39:46,641 --> 01:39:50,077
这回真跑不了啦 外面那么多警察 怎么跑啊
With all the police out there,we really can't escape this time.

1064
01:39:50,228 --> 01:39:53,080
有了 找救兵
Got it! Let's get help.

1065
01:39:59,404 --> 01:40:02,798
哥 有消息了
Brother, any news?

1066
01:40:02,949 --> 01:40:06,719
托尼说人和货 都在医院
Tony says Tang Ren and the gold are all in the hospital.

1067
01:40:08,872 --> 01:40:13,642
哥 咱的苦日子到头了
Brother, our ordeal is coming to an end.

1068
01:40:17,088 --> 01:40:19,273
算他妈到头啦
Finally!

1069
01:41:02,092 --> 01:41:04,276
走啊 进 进
Come on! Hurry up!

1070
01:41:40,880 --> 01:41:43,065
死不瞑目啊
You didn't die in peace.

1071
01:41:48,263 --> 01:41:50,656
安静
Quiet.

1072
01:41:56,396 --> 01:41:59,123
安静 安静 安静
Quiet, quiet, quiet.

1073
01:42:58,124 --> 01:43:01,143
站住
Stop!

1074
01:44:18,663 --> 01:44:25,978
是的 市长您放心 绝不会再有这样的事了
It will never happen again.Yes, Mayor.

1075
01:44:33,303 --> 01:44:36,363
你们听到了
You all heard that.

1076
01:44:36,514 --> 01:44:38,991
这次行动也不是完全没有收获啊
We have actually accomplished something in this operation.

1077
01:44:39,184 --> 01:44:42,911
盗窃团伙也被我们击毙了一个人 抓获了两个人啊
We shot a man dead and arrested two of the robbers.

1078
01:44:43,063 --> 01:44:47,624
所以 你们就炸毁了一个医院
So you blew off a hospital?

1079
01:44:47,776 --> 01:44:52,421
上次是警察局 这次是医院
After the police station,and now it's the hospital.

1080
01:44:52,572 --> 01:44:56,633
抓一个唐仁 你们是不是要毁掉整个曼谷
Do you have to blast the whole Bangkok to get Tang Ren?

1081
01:44:56,785 --> 01:44:59,928
不是不是 我不听你们废话了
No.- I don't want to hear that.

1082
01:45:00,080 --> 01:45:03,474
不是 明天是最后期限
No.- Tomorrow is the deadline.

1083
01:45:03,625 --> 01:45:08,395
你们再抓不到唐仁 就一起滚到COWBOY摸屁股
If you can't get him by then,you can sell yourselves at Cowboy!

1084
01:45:08,546 --> 01:45:10,564
不是NANA吗 滚
I thought you said Nana.- Get out!

1085
01:45:10,715 --> 01:45:14,151
你知道谁是凶手啦 思诺养父 李
Do you know who the murderer is?- Snow's stepfather, Lee.

1086
01:45:14,302 --> 01:45:19,406
啊 怎么会是他呢 他在废车厂工作
How can it be him?- He works at the junk yard.

1087
01:45:19,557 --> 01:45:21,408
巧是巧 可你也不能说
It's a coincidence.But it doesn't mean...

1088
01:45:21,559 --> 01:45:23,494
他就是凶手啊
...he is the murderer.

1089
01:45:23,645 --> 01:45:27,164
四月十三号以前 他请了一周的假
He took a week's leave before April 13th.

1090
01:45:27,315 --> 01:45:30,292
不巧了吧 你怎么知道
Not so much a coincidence, huh?- How do you know that?

1091
01:45:30,443 --> 01:45:32,252
我问了废车厂的华裔经理
I asked the Chinese guy at the junk yard.

1092
01:45:32,404 --> 01:45:35,881
可是黄金呢 我们还剩下两天
But what about the gold?We have two days left.

1093
01:45:36,032 --> 01:45:38,217
我可不想不坐牢就去喂鳄鱼啊
I don't want to go to prison or be fed to the crocodiles.

1094
01:45:38,368 --> 01:45:40,469
这一切都是他精心策划好的
This is all elaborately planned by him.

1095
01:45:40,620 --> 01:45:43,138
我们找到凶手 就找到黄金了
We will find the gold when the murderer is found.

1096
01:45:43,289 --> 01:45:45,057
那我们现在去哪里啊
So where are we going now?

1097
01:45:45,208 --> 01:45:47,309
去找杀人动机
To find out the motive for murder.

1098
01:46:00,682 --> 01:46:02,449
思诺
Snow.

1099
01:46:02,934 --> 01:46:05,119
安眠药 自杀
Sleeping pills. Suicide.

1100
01:46:05,895 --> 01:46:07,663
干什么 人工呼吸啊
What are you doing?- Give her mouth-to-mouth.

1101
01:46:07,856 --> 01:46:10,165
呼个毛线啊 又不是溺水
Cut it out.It's not like she is drowned.

1102
01:46:10,316 --> 01:46:12,543
对 对 赶快送医院啦
Right, let's take her to hospital.

1103
01:46:21,745 --> 01:46:25,222
上面写的什么 杀人动机
What's in there?- The motive.

1104
01:46:25,373 --> 01:46:27,433
什么杀人动机
What motive?

1105
01:46:28,251 --> 01:46:30,811
到底写的什么
What's really in there?

1106
01:46:31,254 --> 01:46:32,771
怎么样
How is she?

1107
01:46:32,922 --> 01:46:37,484
已经给她洗胃了 没危险的
We have pumped her stomach.She is out of danger now.

1108
01:46:37,635 --> 01:46:39,778
没事啦
She is fine.

1109
01:46:43,975 --> 01:46:46,452
阴魂不散啊
They just won't leave us alone.

1110
01:46:55,904 --> 01:46:58,380
小唐 我知道了
Tang, I get it now.

1111
01:46:58,531 --> 01:47:00,257
知道什么了 先找辆车
What?- Let's find a car.

1112
01:47:00,408 --> 01:47:02,134
干什么 去颂帕工坊
What for?- Go to Sompat's Workshop.

1113
01:47:02,285 --> 01:47:04,011
现在 最后再赌一把
Now?- This is our last chance.

1114
01:47:04,162 --> 01:47:05,596
赌什么 黄金
For what?- To find the gold.

1115
01:47:12,545 --> 01:47:14,897
黄SIR 唐仁
Sir, it's Tang Ren.

1116
01:47:17,008 --> 01:47:19,568
在那呢 追 追 追 快 快
Over there.- Get him, go, go, go!

1117
01:47:27,102 --> 01:47:28,952
在前面堵住他们啊
Block them at the next intersection.

1118
01:47:50,542 --> 01:47:53,685
看那里啊 大皇宫啊
Look there! It's the Grand Palace.

1119
01:48:28,246 --> 01:48:31,181
没有我命令不准开枪
Don't shoot. I want him alive.

1120
01:48:39,507 --> 01:48:45,529
唐仁 放弃抵抗 赶紧投降
Tang Ren, give up resistance and surrender now.

1121
01:48:46,431 --> 01:48:49,032
怎么办 看你往哪跑
What do we do now?- You have nowhere to go now.

1122
01:48:50,518 --> 01:48:52,619
冲过去呀
Run them over!

1123
01:49:09,371 --> 01:49:11,346
快跑呀
Run!

1124
01:49:12,332 --> 01:49:14,183
抓活的 抓活的
Get him alive!

1125
01:49:16,169 --> 01:49:17,936
这里啦
Here!

1126
01:49:35,563 --> 01:49:37,498
上车追呀
Get in the car and go after them!

1127
01:49:41,403 --> 01:49:42,836
让一让 让一让
Excuse me! Excuse me!

1128
01:49:42,987 --> 01:49:44,922
这样我们到不了唐人街
We can't get to Chinatown this way.

1129
01:49:45,073 --> 01:49:47,091
快给闫先生打电话啦
Call Mr. Yan.

1130
01:49:56,793 --> 01:49:58,477
谢谢你们把托尼交给我
Thank you for giving Tony to me.

1131
01:49:58,628 --> 01:50:00,354
但你们还剩不到两天
But you only have less than two days.

1132
01:50:00,505 --> 01:50:02,398
不用两天 今天就可以把黄金给你
We don't need two days.We can get your gold back today.

1133
01:50:02,549 --> 01:50:04,775
但是 你要帮我们
But you have to help us!

1134
01:50:19,274 --> 01:50:20,874
快 快
Go, go!

1135
01:50:31,369 --> 01:50:33,262
走开 走开
Get out of the way!

1136
01:50:36,249 --> 01:50:38,058
绕过去 绕过去
Go around them!

1137
01:50:51,014 --> 01:50:53,198
天助我也啦
Help from heaven.

1138
01:51:23,338 --> 01:51:24,897
走 走 走
Let's go!

1139
01:51:41,356 --> 01:51:44,208
自寻死路 给我包围这里
Digging your own grave.Besiege here!

1140
01:51:51,950 --> 01:51:54,343
你到底在找什么 黄金啊
What are you looking for?- The gold.

1141
01:51:54,494 --> 01:51:56,678
不是被我运出去了吗 应该还在这
I moved it.- It should still be here.

1142
01:51:56,830 --> 01:51:58,847
一百公斤东西 不难找
It weighs over 100kg.Shouldn't be so hard to find it.

1143
01:51:58,999 --> 01:52:01,141
警察前面找了好多次啦 都没有找到啊
The police searched several times,but couldn't find anything.

1144
01:52:01,292 --> 01:52:02,810
快点找
Find it!

1145
01:52:02,961 --> 01:52:05,062
找不到呢 找不到就死定啦
What if we can't find it?- We will be dead meat.

1146
01:52:07,465 --> 01:52:09,566
大声公
The megaphone!

1147
01:52:11,386 --> 01:52:13,612
里面的人听着
The men in there,listen carefully.

1148
01:52:13,763 --> 01:52:16,949
不要再抵抗了 你们已经被包围了
Don't kick against the pricks.You are besieged.

1149
01:52:17,100 --> 01:52:21,704
唐仁 我的忍耐是有限度的 现在我数三个数
Tang Ren, I only have so much patience. I'll count to three.

1150
01:52:21,855 --> 01:52:24,081
如果你再不出来 我就要进去了
If you don't come out by then,we will go in.

1151
01:52:24,232 --> 01:52:26,291
我们就要进去啦
We will go in.

1152
01:52:27,444 --> 01:52:28,136
一
One.

1153
01:52:28,536 --> 01:52:29,036
一
One.

1154
01:52:29,487 --> 01:52:32,172
二
Two.

1155
01:52:34,159 --> 01:52:36,468
三
Three.

1156
01:52:56,931 --> 01:52:58,741
唐仁 你脑子是不是有问题
Tang Ren, what's wrong with you?

1157
01:52:58,892 --> 01:53:01,368
拿佛像来当人质呀
Are you holding the Buddha statue hostage?

1158
01:53:01,519 --> 01:53:05,456
黄兰登 你要的黄金在这里呀
Huang Landeng, the gold you are looking for is in here.

1159
01:53:05,732 --> 01:53:08,167
什么鬼啊
What the heck?

1160
01:53:14,824 --> 01:53:16,675
黄金一直在这里
The gold is in here the whole time.

1161
01:53:16,826 --> 01:53:19,261
根本就没有出去过
It never left the place.

1162
01:53:19,412 --> 01:53:22,473
只不过 颂帕把它给铸成佛型了
Sompat made it into a Buddha statue...

1163
01:53:22,624 --> 01:53:25,809
还没来得及告诉他同伙 就被杀死啦
...but he got killed before he could tell his partners.

1164
01:53:25,960 --> 01:53:28,062
五人 盗金团伙
The five suspects of the robbery gang...

1165
01:53:28,213 --> 01:53:30,898
分别是颂帕 还有你的助手托尼
...are Sompat,your assistant Tony...

1166
01:53:31,049 --> 01:53:33,192
昨晚在医院见得那三个人
...and the three guys at the hospital yesterday.

1167
01:53:33,343 --> 01:53:35,652
黄金失主 闫先生可以证明啊
The owner of the stolen gold,Mr. Yan, can prove that.

1168
01:53:37,055 --> 01:53:40,115
可是颂帕还是你杀的 不是我
But you are still the murderer.- No, I'm not.

1169
01:53:40,266 --> 01:53:43,285
凶手另有其人 我们已经找到他了
It's someone else.- We have found him.

1170
01:53:43,645 --> 01:53:47,122
可以马上带你去找他 当面指证
And we can take you to him now.- To testify against him.

1171
01:53:59,536 --> 01:54:02,721
黄兰登 我知道你是铁血神探
Huang Landeng,I know you are the Hot Fuzz.

1172
01:54:02,914 --> 01:54:07,101
难道你不想知道事情的真相吗 很刺激的
Don't you want to know the truth?- It's thrilling.

1173
01:54:07,252 --> 01:54:11,313
我再相信你一次 别跟我耍花样啊
I'll believe you one more time.Don't play tricks with me.

1174
01:54:18,722 --> 01:54:20,531
黄金案归你了 不是我
The gold robbery case is yours.- What?

1175
01:54:20,682 --> 01:54:23,033
凶杀案当然是我的啦 我
And the homicide case is mine.- I...

1176
01:54:23,184 --> 01:54:26,245
副局长当然也是我啦
And I will be the deputy chief, too.

1177
01:54:29,649 --> 01:54:32,126
喝喝这个补补脑
Here, it's brain-boosting.

1178
01:54:33,695 --> 01:54:38,424
你还有什么不明白的吗 一会儿 你和凶手对质
Do you have any questions?You confront the murderer.

1179
01:54:38,658 --> 01:54:41,510
为什么又是我 不是你呀
Why me again?

1180
01:54:41,661 --> 01:54:44,555
你 你说呢
What do you think?

1181
01:54:47,667 --> 01:54:49,435
你不该这么做的
You shouldn't have done this.

1182
01:54:49,586 --> 01:54:52,604
你好啊 雇主先生 你什么意思
Nice to meet you.- What are you talking about?

1183
01:54:56,176 --> 01:55:00,028
我们见过 就在颂帕死的那天晚上 你忘记啦
We met on the night Sompat was killed. Don't you remember that?

1184
01:55:00,722 --> 01:55:04,199
我不明白你在说什么
I don't know what you are talking about.

1185
01:55:05,018 --> 01:55:09,038
这话好像是 烂俗电影里大反派的回答
It sounds like a line of the villain in a lame film.

1186
01:55:09,314 --> 01:55:12,583
女士们 先生们 我想说的是
Ladies and gentlemen,I would like to point out that...

1187
01:55:12,901 --> 01:55:17,796
颂帕被杀案 和黄金失窃案 这本来就是两个案子
...the murder of Sompat and the robbery are two different cases.

1188
01:55:17,947 --> 01:55:22,092
只不过恰巧的是 颂帕也是黄金盗匪之一
But coincidentally,Sompat was one of the robbers.

1189
01:55:22,243 --> 01:55:27,014
所以这个案子 才给我和黄警探带来了这么多的麻烦
So it brought so much trouble to Detective Huang and me.

1190
01:55:27,165 --> 01:55:31,435
说重点 故事 要从死者死前一周
Get to the point!- The story began from April 7th...

1191
01:55:31,586 --> 01:55:34,605
也就是说四月七日那天开始讲起
...which is seven days before the murder.

1192
01:55:35,256 --> 01:55:39,359
那天 我接到了一个陌生人的电话
On that day, I got a phone call from a stranger.

1193
01:55:39,511 --> 01:55:41,195
你好
Hello.

1194
01:55:41,346 --> 01:55:45,741
现在我知道了 打电话的人就是这位李先生
Now I know that the caller is Mr. Lee here.

1195
01:55:45,892 --> 01:55:50,245
这是他 计划的一小部分 先找一个合适的替死鬼
It's a part of his plan.Find a fall guy first.

1196
01:55:50,397 --> 01:55:52,956
我按约定到了颂帕工坊
I went to Sompat's Workshop as asked.

1197
01:55:53,108 --> 01:55:55,626
我以为见到的是死者颂帕
I thought the guy I met was Sompat.

1198
01:55:55,777 --> 01:55:59,963
而我见到的 却是这位李先生
But the man I really saw was Mr. Lee.

1199
01:56:00,115 --> 01:56:02,716
不可能 他怎么进入现场的
It's impossible.How did he get into the workshop?

1200
01:56:02,867 --> 01:56:04,885
监视器根本没有拍到他
He didn't even show up in the footages.

1201
01:56:05,036 --> 01:56:07,721
我们这位李先生 知道监视器内容
Mr. Lee knew that the video footages...

1202
01:56:07,872 --> 01:56:09,932
七天就会自动覆盖
...would be automatically overwritten every seven days.

1203
01:56:10,083 --> 01:56:14,311
所以他提前一周 就藏在了颂帕的家里
So he hid in Sompat's workshop a week in advance.

1204
01:56:16,798 --> 01:56:21,110
他在床下留下的脚印 暴露了他的踪迹
The footprint he had left under the bed gave him away.

1205
01:56:21,261 --> 01:56:25,155
四月十四日晚 我们的李先生算好了时间
On the night of April 14th,with careful timing...

1206
01:56:25,306 --> 01:56:30,035
在我要来之前 他用降魔杵杀死了颂帕
...Mr. Lee killed Sompat with the vajra before I showed up.

1207
01:56:30,186 --> 01:56:32,454
李先生那晚并没有开灯
Mr. Lee didn't turn on the light that night.

1208
01:56:32,647 --> 01:56:36,041
而点的却是蜡烛 这样便于迷惑我
He lit a candle instead because it could not only dazzle me...

1209
01:56:36,192 --> 01:56:38,252
更能让蜡烛自己燃尽
...but also burn out itself.

1210
01:56:38,570 --> 01:56:43,590
而他 早就换上了和颂帕一样的服装 头套 眼镜
And he dressed like Sompat,and put on wig and glasses...

1211
01:56:43,742 --> 01:56:47,553
就是为了让我以为 他就是颂帕
...to make me believe that he was Sompat.

1212
01:56:47,704 --> 01:56:50,597
很快 我就如约而至了
Soon, I arrived in time.

1213
01:56:50,749 --> 01:56:52,975
取货
I'm here for a pick up.

1214
01:56:54,502 --> 01:56:56,895
最最精彩的就要来了
Now is the highlight of the story.

1215
01:56:57,047 --> 01:56:59,690
我们一直百思不得其解
What we couldn't figure out was...

1216
01:56:59,841 --> 01:57:01,775
凶手是如何离开现场的呢
...how the killer left the crime scene.

1217
01:57:01,926 --> 01:57:04,945
就在刚刚 我撞翻了医院的手推车
Just a while ago, when I knocked over a trolley in the hospital...

1218
01:57:05,096 --> 01:57:07,072
我才想到了答案
...I figured it out.

1219
01:57:07,223 --> 01:57:09,867
这招简直就是太完美了
This is so perfect.

1220
01:57:10,018 --> 01:57:14,955
他要让我送的货 根本就是他自己
What he asked me to pick up was himself.

1221
01:57:15,106 --> 01:57:19,126
他钻进木箱后 打开了工作室的音响
He got into the box and turned on the speaker in the studio...

1222
01:57:19,277 --> 01:57:22,504
让我误以为 继续工作的是颂帕
...to make me believe that the working man was Sompat.

1223
01:57:22,655 --> 01:57:26,592
其实 我看到的不过是具尸体
But in fact,what I saw was a dead body.

1224
01:57:26,743 --> 01:57:29,303
他从里面锁住了箱子
He locked the box from inside.

1225
01:57:29,454 --> 01:57:31,638
我以为我运出去的是佛像
I thought I left with a Buddha statue.

1226
01:57:31,790 --> 01:57:34,558
你们以为我运出去的是黄金
And you thought I left with the gold.

1227
01:57:34,709 --> 01:57:40,981
谁都没想到 我运出去的却是他 杀人凶手
But no one ever thought that I left with him, the murderer.

1228
01:57:47,222 --> 01:57:49,990
杰克・福翠尔《遗失的镭》中
In Jacques Futrelle's "The Problem of the Lost Radium"...

1229
01:57:50,141 --> 01:57:53,410
凶手就是藏在皮箱里潜入研究所的
...the murderer snuck into the lab lying in a suitcase.

1230
01:57:53,561 --> 01:57:56,288
青崎有吾 写的《体育馆杀人》
In Yugo Aosaki's "Murder in the Gym"...

1231
01:57:56,481 --> 01:58:00,626
凶手也是躲在 一辆手推车里离开现场的
...the murderer left the scene in a trolley.

1232
01:58:00,777 --> 01:58:05,506
这种桥段 在我们侦探推理界里 并不新鲜
It's not something new in our detective world.

1233
01:58:07,909 --> 01:58:11,887
而我们这位凶手 利用监控录像
The murderer took advantage of the surveillance footages...

1234
01:58:12,038 --> 01:58:15,557
把我包装成了嫌疑犯
...to set me up,and took advantage of me...

1235
01:58:15,709 --> 01:58:17,518
利用嫌疑犯把真凶带出了现场
...to bring the real murderer out.

1236
01:58:17,669 --> 01:58:21,146
我不得不说 干得实在是太漂亮了
I have to say,he did such a good job.

1237
01:58:21,339 --> 01:58:26,485
要不是他 千算万算只算错了一步 替死鬼找到了
If he didn't miss a step and took the Number One detective...

1238
01:58:26,636 --> 01:58:30,155
唐人街第一神探 我的身上
...of Chinatown as his fall guy...

1239
01:58:30,306 --> 01:58:34,493
这个案子 简直就是 天衣无缝
...the crime he committed would have been perfect.

1240
01:58:34,644 --> 01:58:37,538
听着是精彩 但李先生的杀人动机在哪呢
It sounds interesting.But what's his motive?

1241
01:58:39,149 --> 01:58:44,169
你一定知道 颂帕的儿子 丹 一年前离奇失踪了
You must know that Sompat's son,Dan went missing a year ago.

1242
01:58:44,320 --> 01:58:48,215
知道啊 可是丹就是这位
Yes.- But what you don't know is...

1243
01:58:48,366 --> 01:58:51,510
思诺小姑娘的同学 你一定就不知道了
...that Dan is Snow's schoolmate.

1244
01:58:51,661 --> 01:58:57,975

It led us to another sad story.

1245
01:59:02,797 --> 01:59:08,819

You must have read this journal.- Whose journal is it?

1246
01:59:10,096 --> 01:59:12,698

Hers. She tried to burn it...

1247
01:59:12,849 --> 01:59:15,617

...before she attempted suicide,but we stopped her in time.

1248
01:59:15,810 --> 01:59:20,330

What's in the journal?- The motive for murder.

1249
01:59:21,399 --> 01:59:24,543

Snow's journal keeps track of...

1250
01:59:24,819 --> 01:59:27,963

...Sompat's psychological changes after his son had gone missing.

1251
01:59:28,114 --> 01:59:31,341

He started to stalk his son's schoolmates.

1252
01:59:31,493 --> 01:59:34,428

It's so creepy.- What's creepier is that...

1253
01:59:34,579 --> 01:59:38,223

...he brought Snow home and raped her.

1254
01:59:40,502 --> 01:59:42,853

Shut up!

1255
01:59:43,171 --> 01:59:45,481

The girl felt ashamed to tell anybody...

1256
01:59:45,632 --> 01:59:48,817

...so she kept the painful experience in her journal.

1257
01:59:48,968 --> 01:59:54,156

But unfortunately, her stepfather read the journal one day.

1258
01:59:54,307 --> 01:59:57,534

Even if what's in the journal is true...

1259
01:59:57,686 --> 02:00:00,454

...you can't testify against me.

1260
02:00:00,605 --> 02:00:05,417

I have never gone to that workshop or met Sompat.

1261
02:00:06,319 --> 02:00:09,380

That van comes from the junk yard.

1262
02:00:09,531 --> 02:00:13,592

And you work there, don't you?- It's just a coincidence.

1263
02:00:13,743 --> 02:00:15,886

Where is the evidence?

1264
02:00:16,037 --> 02:00:18,347

We fought against the real murderer last night.

1265
02:00:18,498 --> 02:00:22,476

If I've got it right,your right arm is injured.

1266
02:00:24,087 --> 02:00:30,567

Even if I am, it's from an accident at work a few days ago.

1267
02:00:33,304 --> 02:00:35,364

Look at you. Your eyebrows are pointy at the front...

1268
02:00:35,515 --> 02:00:37,574

...and wide at rear. You have a black mole at your Life Palace.

1269
02:00:37,726 --> 02:00:39,618

You have bloodshot eyes and crow's feet.

1270
02:00:39,769 --> 02:00:42,246

Someone having a face like that is either violent or wicked.

1271
02:00:42,397 --> 02:00:46,458

You want evidence, don't you?

1272
02:00:48,570 --> 02:00:51,964

The Bluetooth-enabled speaker can remember the users.

1273
02:00:52,115 --> 02:00:56,093

Turn on your phone and see if it connects automatically.

1274
02:00:58,663 --> 02:01:02,850

Dad, is this true?

1275
02:01:05,170 --> 02:01:08,230

I don't regret this.

1276
02:01:09,924 --> 02:01:11,859

I love you.

1277
02:01:15,055 --> 02:01:22,202

I know.- No, you don't know. I love you.

1278
02:01:50,507 --> 02:01:54,276

He has retrieved the stolen gold...

1279
02:01:54,427 --> 02:01:58,781

...and killed the murderer who tried to escape.

1280
02:01:58,932 --> 02:02:06,080

Let's welcome our new deputy chief of Chinatown Police, Kon Tai.

1281
02:02:30,380 --> 02:02:32,189

I hope you will come to Thailand again.

1282
02:02:32,340 --> 02:02:35,234

Thank you.- You must come for our wedding.

1283
02:02:35,385 --> 02:02:37,653

Who says I will marry you,pauper?

1284
02:02:37,804 --> 02:02:40,155

I have to call you aunt now?- Of course.

1285
02:02:41,474 --> 02:02:45,369

Aunt? Isn't he your cousin?Aren't you born in the 90s?

1286
02:02:45,520 --> 02:02:48,163

Goodbye!- Liars!

1287
02:02:55,572 --> 02:02:58,298

What? You don't want to leave?

1288
02:02:58,450 --> 02:03:01,468

What will you miss more,Thailand or the Thai people?

1289
02:03:01,619 --> 02:03:05,347

What are you talking about?- You don't want to leave me.

1290
02:03:08,626 --> 02:03:10,811

Stop, stop!

1291
02:03:12,088 --> 02:03:15,482

What is written on that signboard?

1292
02:03:15,633 --> 02:03:17,776

It's the name of that bar.

1293
02:03:17,927 --> 02:03:21,321

It's the most famous gay bar in Bangkok.

1294
02:03:21,806 --> 02:03:24,825

Sompat got divorced with his wife nine years ago.

1295
02:03:24,976 --> 02:03:26,785

The room is neither messy nor smelly.

1296
02:03:26,936 --> 02:03:29,121

He must be a sissy or a gay.

1297
02:03:41,993 --> 02:03:45,137

I thought you were going home today.

1298
02:03:45,705 --> 02:03:48,390

I want to tell you a story.

1299
02:03:48,541 --> 02:03:51,477

Both you and that uncle love stories.

1300
02:03:53,380 --> 02:03:58,108

A boy went missing. His father had been looking for him.

1301
02:03:59,594 --> 02:04:01,987

He suspected that his son was dead.

1302
02:04:02,138 --> 02:04:06,950

More importantly, he suspected the murderer of his son...

1303
02:04:07,102 --> 02:04:10,079

...might be a girl.

1304
02:04:24,202 --> 02:04:26,637

The girl found out about it.

1305
02:04:26,788 --> 02:04:29,431

She was afraid that she'd be exposed.

1306
02:04:29,582 --> 02:04:33,185

So she decided to get rid of the father.

1307
02:04:33,336 --> 02:04:35,979

She knew about the perverted love her stepfather had for her.

1308
02:04:36,131 --> 02:04:40,401

So she fabricated a journal...

1309
02:04:42,387 --> 02:04:45,280

...and let her stepfather read it intentionally.

1310
02:04:49,602 --> 02:04:53,956

I wondered what was in the part that was ripped off.

1311
02:04:54,107 --> 02:04:56,917

What was it that she didn't want us to know?

1312
02:04:57,068 --> 02:04:59,336

Maybe it was the way the murder was committed.

1313
02:05:02,699 --> 02:05:08,762

If I could kill him,I'd find a scrapped van...

1314
02:05:08,913 --> 02:05:12,391

...and a fall guy first.

1315
02:05:12,542 --> 02:05:14,518

I'd get into his house...

1316
02:05:14,669 --> 02:05:17,146

...before the footages are automatically overwritten.

1317
02:05:21,134 --> 02:05:24,695

I'd make him suffer thousands of times worse than I did.

1318
02:05:33,897 --> 02:05:36,665

The girl didn't expect that we'd come to her.

1319
02:05:36,816 --> 02:05:41,211

So she changed her plan and used us...

1320
02:05:41,363 --> 02:05:43,714

...to get rid of her perverted stepfather.

1321
02:05:48,244 --> 02:05:51,805

The timing the journal showed up and its burning speed...

1322
02:05:51,956 --> 02:05:54,058

...were exactly on spot.

1323
02:05:54,209 --> 02:05:57,811

But the girl didn't know that...

1324
02:05:57,962 --> 02:06:01,607

...the man she framed a rape against is a gay.

1325
02:06:01,800 --> 02:06:03,650

You don't stutter now.

1326
02:06:03,802 --> 02:06:07,362

Of course,these are all hypothesized.

1327
02:06:07,514 --> 02:06:10,491

No evidence can prove the sexual orientation of a dead man.

1328
02:06:10,642 --> 02:06:14,244

But I don't get it.- Forget it.

1329
02:06:15,063 --> 02:06:18,832

This book says,while we are individual lives...

1330
02:06:18,983 --> 02:06:21,627

...the summation of good and evil is invariant.

1331
02:06:21,778 --> 02:06:25,714

Everyone plays his role from birth.

1332
02:06:25,865 --> 02:06:29,510

Some of them are good,and some of them are evil.

1333
02:06:29,786 --> 02:06:32,221

What are you?

1334
02:06:36,918 --> 02:06:40,020

Should the villain smile like this?

1335
02:07:07,490 --> 02:07:09,800

So this is it?

1336
02:07:09,951 --> 02:07:15,264

There's nothing else I can do.- Nobody cares about the truth.

1337
02:07:15,415 --> 02:07:19,852

They only believe the truth they want to see.

1338
02:07:22,380 --> 02:07:26,233

Good and evil are incompatible.

1339
02:07:26,384 --> 02:07:31,155

When there is evil,there has to be good.

1340
02:07:31,306 --> 02:07:33,323

Yes. There are so many mysteries.

1341
02:07:33,475 --> 02:07:36,285

As detectives of Chinatown,we have to uphold justice...

1342
02:07:36,436 --> 02:07:38,954

...punish the evil and praise the good.

1343
02:07:41,232 --> 02:07:42,833

The plane!

1344
02:07:45,153 --> 02:07:49,089

What should I do?- How would I know?

1345
02:07:51,159 --> 02:07:53,427

So I have to endorse the ticket.

1346
02:07:55,413 --> 02:07:58,140

Or you can stay for another seven days.

1347
02:07:58,291 --> 02:08:01,518

I'll take you to the Grand Palace tomorrow.

1348
02:08:00,670 --> 02:08:02,395

No!


